cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.SY 

The paper focuses on improving environment simulators using recurrent neural networks, which is a topic that falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of high-dimensional pixel observations and image generation also suggests a connection to computer vision (cs.CV). Additionally, the paper discusses the application of the approach to diverse environments, including games and 3D mazes, which could be related to robotics (cs.RO) and systems and control (cs.SY).
